<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome 🎉 To NestJs</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f6f8;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      .header {
        background: #4f46e5;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        background: #4f46e5;
        color: #fff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome, <%= name %> 🎉</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>

        <p>
          We’re really excited to have you join us! 🙌 Your account has been successfully created,
          and you're now part of our community.
        </p>

        <p>
          You can get started right away by exploring your dashboard and setting up your profile.
        </p>

        <a href="<%= url %>" class="button">Get Started</a>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px">
          If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email—we’re always here to help.
        </p>

        <p>
          Cheers, <br />
          The <%= appName %> Team 💙
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>© <%= year %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
